OL,3,CMan, 64, convicted of murdering friend
OL,4,Cin her home before stealing from her
OL,6,FA man has been found guilty of murder
OL,7,Fafter stabbing his friend 11 times in
OL,8,Fthe neck in her own home before
OL,9,Fstealing money from her.
OL,11,FThomas Turner, 64, who is originally
OL,12,Ffrom Uttoxeter, was convicted at
OL,13,FLoughborough Crown Court today.
OL,15,FHe had been drinking and smoking with
OL,16,Fhis friend Mandy Riley at her home in
OL,17,FWest Yorkshire on 4 June 2025.
OL,19,FPolice believe Turner 'lost his
OL,20,Ftemper' after asking Ms Riley for
OL,21,Fmoney, which she refused.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/6
