PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1775153467
OL,3,CMan, 64, convicted of murdering friend
OL,4,Cin her home before stealing from her
OL,6,FHe then stabbed her multiple times
OL,7,Fbefore trying to cover his tracks by
OL,8,Fheading to another friend's house and
OL,9,Fwashing his clothes.
OL,11,FAfter killing the 47-year-old, Turner
OL,12,Fstole money from her handbag.
OL,14,FTurner left Ms Riley's flat at around
OL,15,F10.30pm and soon after, used the money
OL,16,Fhe had stolen to buy alcohol and drugs.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1775153467
OL,3,CMan, 64, convicted of murdering friend
OL,4,Cin her home before stealing from her
OL,6,FLater that morning, he was seen going
OL,7,Finto the house of another friend in
OL,8,FDuncan Road, where he put a bag full
OL,9,Fof clothes into the washing machine
OL,10,Fbefore leaving without speaking to
OL,11,Fanyone.
OL,13,FMs Riley's body was discovered just
OL,14,Fafter 10.30am on 5 June by another
OL,15,Ffriend who had been due to take her to
OL,16,Fa medical appointment but could not
OL,17,Fget hold of her.
OL,19,FTurner was arrested just before 5pm on
OL,20,F5 June on suspicion of murder.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
