OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1775153467
OL,3,CMan, 64, convicted of murdering friend
OL,4,Cin her home before stealing from her
OL,6,FWhile in police custody he refused to
OL,7,Fleave his cell to be interviewed and
OL,8,Fwhen questioned in custody, remained
OL,9,Fsilent.
OL,11,FForensic tests showed Turner's DNA was
OL,12,Fon the strap and outside of Ms Riley's
OL,13,Fpurse and a distinctive crack pipe
OL,14,Fbelonging to Ms Riley was found at the
OL,15,FDuncan Road address with Turner's
OL,16,Fbelongings.
OL,18,FTurner was charged with Ms Riley's
OL,19,Fmurder on 8 June 2025.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/6
