PN,37105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1775153467
OL,3,CMan, 64, convicted of murdering friend
OL,4,Cin her home before stealing from her
OL,6,FDetective Chief Inspector Laura
OL,7,FSanders, who led the investigation for
OL,8,FDerbyshire Police, said: "Mandy Riley
OL,9,Fwas killed in the one place she should
OL,10,Fhave felt safe, and by someone she
OL,11,Ftrusted as a friend.
OL,13,F"Having murdered Mandy, Turner then
OL,14,Fstole from her before using the money
OL,15,Fto feed his drink and drug habit.
OL,17,F"He has repeatedly denied murdering
OL,18,Fher, but the jury has seen through his
OL,19,Flies and Turner is now facing a
OL,20,Flengthy spell behind bars, where he
OL,21,Fbelongs."
OL,26,@pD@ZOUuD@AOUyD@AOU}D@IO]
